---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "Representing and Supporting General Practice in Manchester"
description: "Manchester LMC is the statutory representative body for approximately 400 GPs across 87 practices in Manchester."
mainClass: page-content
showContactStrip: true
showDisclaimer: true
---

  <!-- ── Hero ─────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="hero" aria-labelledby="hero-heading">
    <div class="hero-bg"></div>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-inner">
        <div class="hero-content">
          <p class="hero-eyebrow">
            <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/></svg>
            Manchester LMC
          </p>
          <h1 id="hero-heading">Representing and Supporting General Practice in Manchester</h1>
          <p class="hero-lead">
            Your statutory representative body — standing up for 400 GPs across 87 practices, providing expert guidance, confidential support, and a strong collective voice for primary care.
          </p>
          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a href="/support/" class="btn btn--primary btn--lg">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07A19.5 19.5 0 0 1 4.69 12a19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 3.6 1.18H6.6a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72c.127.96.361 1.903.7 2.81a2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L7.51 8.69a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45c.907.339 1.85.573 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 15.92z"/></svg>
              How We Can Help
            </a>
            <a href="/members/" class="btn btn--secondary btn--lg">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H8a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"/></svg>
              Member Login
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-visual" aria-hidden="true">
          <img src="/assets/images/logo.svg" alt="" class="hero-logo-mark">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── Role Selector ──────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="role-strip" aria-labelledby="role-heading">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 id="role-heading">I am a…</h2>
      <div class="role-cards">

        <a href="/support/#partner" class="role-card">
          <div class="role-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="7" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="M16 21V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span class="role-card-title">GP Partner</span>
          <span class="role-card-sub">Contracts, governance &amp; representation</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/support/#salaried" class="role-card">
          <div class="role-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H8a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span class="role-card-title">Salaried GP</span>
          <span class="role-card-sub">Employment rights &amp; support</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/support/#locum" class="role-card">
          <div class="role-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span class="role-card-title">Locum GP</span>
          <span class="role-card-sub">Membership, IR35 &amp; LMC levy</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/support/#manager" class="role-card">
          <div class="role-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/><line x1="16" y1="13" x2="8" y2="13"/><line x1="16" y1="17" x2="8" y2="17"/><polyline points="10 9 9 9 8 9"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span class="role-card-title">Practice Manager</span>
          <span class="role-card-sub">Operational guidance &amp; HR</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/support/#nurse" class="role-card">
          <div class="role-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4.8 2.3A.3.3 0 1 0 5 2H4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v5a6 6 0 0 0 6 6v0a6 6 0 0 0 6-6V4a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-1a.2.2 0 1 0 .3.3"/><path d="M8 15v1a6 6 0 0 0 6 6v0a6 6 0 0 0 6-6v-4"/><circle cx="20" cy="10" r="2"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span class="role-card-title">Nurse / AHP</span>
          <span class="role-card-sub">ARRS roles &amp; wellbeing</span>
        </a>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── Statistics ──────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="stats-banner" aria-label="Key statistics">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="stats-grid">
        <div class="stat-item reveal">
          <div class="stat-number" data-count="400" data-suffix="+">0</div>
          <div class="stat-label">GPs Represented</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item reveal reveal-delay-1">
          <div class="stat-number" data-count="87">0</div>
          <div class="stat-label">GP Practices</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <div class="stat-number" data-count="1911" data-no-format>0</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Established</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item reveal reveal-delay-3">
          <div class="stat-number" data-count="100" data-suffix="+">0</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Years of Service</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── Latest News ─────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="section" aria-labelledby="news-heading">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header flex-between">
        <div>
          <span class="section-eyebrow">Stay Informed</span>
          <h2 id="news-heading">Latest News</h2>
        </div>
        <a href="/news/" class="link-arrow">
          All News
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="grid-3" role="list">
        {% for article in collections.featuredNews | limit(3) %}
          {% include "partials/news-card.njk" %}
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── Upcoming Events ─────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="section section--neutral" aria-labelledby="events-heading">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header flex-between">
        <div>
          <span class="section-eyebrow">Your Calendar</span>
          <h2 id="events-heading">Upcoming Events</h2>
        </div>
        <a href="/events/" class="link-arrow">
          Full Calendar
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:var(--space-4);">

        <div class="event-item reveal">
          <div class="event-date-badge">
            <span class="event-date-day">25</span>
            <span class="event-date-month">Feb</span>
          </div>
          <div class="event-content">
            <h4><a href="/events/">Manchester LMC Partners Meeting</a></h4>
            <div class="event-meta">
              <span class="event-meta-item">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg>
                18:30 – 20:00
              </span>
              <span class="event-meta-item">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/></svg>
                Manchester Medical Society, Dover St
              </span>
            </div>
            <p class="event-desc">Quarterly partners meeting. Agenda includes GP contract updates, local collective action guidance, and ICB liaison.</p>
          </div>
          <a href="/events/" class="btn btn--outline btn--sm" style="flex-shrink:0;align-self:center;">Register</a>
        </div>

        <div class="event-item reveal reveal-delay-1">
          <div class="event-date-badge">
            <span class="event-date-day">4</span>
            <span class="event-date-month">Mar</span>
          </div>
          <div class="event-content">
            <h4><a href="/events/">Locum GP Network Meeting</a></h4>
            <div class="event-meta">
              <span class="event-meta-item">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg>
                13:00 – 14:30
              </span>
              <span class="event-meta-item">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21"/></svg>
                Online (Microsoft Teams)
              </span>
            </div>
            <p class="event-desc">Open meeting for locum GPs in Manchester — LMC levy, IR35 updates, and peer networking. All locums welcome.</p>
          </div>
          <a href="/events/" class="btn btn--outline btn--sm" style="flex-shrink:0;align-self:center;">Register</a>
        </div>

        <div class="event-item reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <div class="event-date-badge">
            <span class="event-date-day">18</span>
            <span class="event-date-month">Mar</span>
          </div>
          <div class="event-content">
            <h4><a href="/events/">CQC Inspection Readiness Workshop</a></h4>
            <div class="event-meta">
              <span class="event-meta-item">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg>
                10:00 – 12:00
              </span>
              <span class="event-meta-item">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/></svg>
                Manchester Central Library
              </span>
            </div>
            <p class="event-desc">Practical workshop on CQC's new single assessment framework. For GPs, practice managers, and clinical leads.</p>
          </div>
          <a href="/events/" class="btn btn--outline btn--sm" style="flex-shrink:0;align-self:center;">Register</a>
        </div>

      </div><!-- /events list -->
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── Services Grid ───────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="section" aria-labelledby="services-heading">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header section-header--center">
        <span class="section-eyebrow">What We Offer</span>
        <h2 id="services-heading">How Manchester LMC Supports You</h2>
        <p>From expert guidance to confidential support, we're here every step of the way.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid-3">

        <a href="/guidance/" class="service-card reveal">
          <div class="service-card-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/><line x1="16" y1="13" x2="8" y2="13"/><line x1="16" y1="17" x2="8" y2="17"/><polyline points="10 9 9 9 8 9"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Guidance Library</h3>
          <p>Access our searchable library of clinical guidance, contractual documents, CQC templates, and policy resources.</p>
          <span class="service-card-link">Browse resources
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg>
          </span>
        </a>

        <a href="/support/" class="service-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
          <div class="service-card-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07A19.5 19.5 0 0 1 4.69 12a19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 3.6 1.18H6.6a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72c.127.96.361 1.903.7 2.81a2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L7.51 8.69a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45c.907.339 1.85.573 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 15.92z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>GP Support</h3>
          <p>Confidential advisory service for GMC concerns, complaints, suspension, partnership disputes, and CQC inspections.</p>
          <span class="service-card-link">Get support
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg>
          </span>
        </a>

        <a href="/support/wellbeing/" class="service-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <div class="service-card-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0 0-7.78z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Wellbeing Hub</h3>
          <p>Mental health resources, peer support programmes, free apps, and crisis contacts for GPs and practice staff.</p>
          <span class="service-card-link">Explore wellbeing
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg>
          </span>
        </a>

        <a href="/vacancies/" class="service-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
          <div class="service-card-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><rect x="2" y="7" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="M16 21V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Vacancies</h3>
          <p>Browse GP and primary care vacancies across Manchester, or post your own practice vacancy to reach local candidates.</p>
          <span class="service-card-link">View jobs
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg>
          </span>
        </a>

        <a href="/events/" class="service-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <div class="service-card-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><line x1="16" y1="2" x2="16" y2="6"/><line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="6"/><line x1="3" y1="10" x2="21" y2="10"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Events &amp; Meetings</h3>
          <p>LMC committee meetings, educational events, and networking sessions — in-person and online throughout the year.</p>
          <span class="service-card-link">See calendar
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg>
          </span>
        </a>

        <a href="/members/" class="service-card reveal reveal-delay-3">
          <div class="service-card-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2"/><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Members Area</h3>
          <p>Subscriber-only resources, meeting agendas, minutes archive, open forum, and the Manchester GP Network.</p>
          <span class="service-card-link">Members login
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg>
          </span>
        </a>

      </div><!-- /grid-3 -->
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── Latest Newsletter ───────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="section section--neutral" aria-labelledby="newsletter-heading">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="newsletter-card reveal">
        <div class="newsletter-card-body">
          <p class="newsletter-card-eyebrow">Newsletter</p>
          <h3 id="newsletter-heading">Manchester LMC Newsletter — Winter 2025/26</h3>
          <p>Our quarterly newsletter covers the latest from general practice in Manchester: contract updates, local policy news, wellbeing resources, and LMC committee actions.</p>
          <div style="display:flex;gap:var(--space-4);flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:var(--space-6);">
            <a href="/news/#newsletters" class="btn btn--secondary">Download Issue (PDF)</a>
            <a href="/news/#newsletters" class="btn btn--outline btn--secondary" style="border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);color:rgba(255,255,255,0.85);">View Archive</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="newsletter-card-download">
          <div class="newsletter-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/><line x1="12" y1="18" x2="12" y2="12"/><polyline points="9 15 12 18 15 15"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span style="font-size:0.8125rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6);">Issue 42 · Winter 2025</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── Twitter / Social embed area ────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="section" aria-labelledby="social-heading">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header section-header--center" style="margin-bottom:var(--space-8);">
        <span class="section-eyebrow">Social</span>
        <h2 id="social-heading">Follow Us on X (Twitter)</h2>
      </div>
      <div style="max-width:550px;margin:0 auto;">
        <!-- Placeholder for Twitter/X embed widget -->
        <div style="background:var(--colour-neutral);border:1px solid var(--colour-border);border-radius:var(--radius-xl);padding:var(--space-10);text-align:center;color:var(--colour-muted);">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" style="margin:0 auto var(--space-4);" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M18.244 2.25h3.308l-7.227 8.26 8.502 11.24H16.17l-4.714-6.231-5.401 6.231H2.739l7.734-8.835L1.254 2.25H8.08l4.26 5.632zm-1.161 17.52h1.833L7.084 4.126H5.117z"/></svg>
          <p style="margin-bottom:var(--space-4);">Latest tweets from <strong>@ManchesterLMC</strong></p>
          <a href="https://twitter.com/manchesterlmc" class="btn btn--outline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">View on X / Twitter</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
